ock fight: Bench |work=The Hindu |date=14 January 2011 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|14 January 2011}} |location=Chennai, India}}\n* {{cite web |title=MA Chidambaram Stadium |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/india/content/ground/58008.html |publisher=Espncricinfo |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2012 |ref={{sfnRef|MA Chidambaram Stadium|2012}} }}\n* {{cite web |title=Srinivas Venkataraghavan |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/india/content/ground/58008.html |publisher=Espncricinfo |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Srinivas Venkataraghavan|2012}} }}\n* {{cite web |title=Kris Srikkanth |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/34103.html |publisher=Espncricinfo |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Kris Srikkanth|2012}} }}\n* {{cite web |title=Lakshmipathy Balaji |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/26829.html |publisher=Espncricinfo |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Lakshmipathy Balaji|2012}} }}\n* {{cite web |title=Ravichandran Ashwin |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/26421.html |publisher=Espncricinfo |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Ravichandran Ashwin|2012}} }}\n* {{cite web |title=Ravichandran Ashwin |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/26421.html |publisher=Espncricinfo |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Ravichandran Ashwin|2012}} }}\n* {{cite web |title=Laxman Sivaramakrishnan |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/ci/content/player/34074.html |publisher=Espncricinfo |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Laxman Sivaramakrishnan|2012}} }}\n* {{cite web |title=Primary census abstract 2001 |url=http://census2001.tn.nic.in/pca2001.aspx |publisher=Directorate of Census Operations &nbsp;\u2013 Tamil Nadu |accessdate=8 June 2012 |year=2001 |ref={{sfnRef|Census of Tamil Nadu|2001}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110217153857/http://census2001.tn.nic.in/pca2001.aspx |archivedate=17 February 2