01 |publisher=Union Ministry of Social Justice |year=2001 |accessdate=4 July 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Human Development Index|2001}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722093933/http://socialjustice.nic.in/pdf/tab16.pdf |archivedate=22 July 2013  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://mospi.nic.in/mospi_new/upload/census_2012/EC_main_2012.htm |title=Sixth Economic Census |publisher=Ministry of Statistics and Programme Implementation, Gov of India |year=2012 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Sixth Economic Census}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113225608/http://www.mospi.nic.in/mospi_new/upload/census_2012/EC_main_2012.htm |archivedate=13 November 2012  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=29977 |title=Press Information Bureau English Releases |publisher=Pib.nic.in |year=2012 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Press Information Bureau releases|2012}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=https://whc.unesco.org/en/list |title=UNESCO World Heritage List |publisher=Whc.unesco.org |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnref|UNESCO|2012}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://asc-india.org/maps/hazard/haz-tamil-nadu.htm |title=Amateur Seismic Centre, Pune |publisher=Asc-india.org |date=30 March 2007 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Amateur Seismic Centre|2007}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.forests.tn.nic.in/WildBiodiversity/wildbiodiversity_home.html |title=Biodiversity, Tamil Nadu Dept. of Forests |publisher=Forests.tn.nic.in |year=2012 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Biodiversity of Tamil Nadu|2012}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206055559/http://www.forests.tn.nic.in/WildBiodiversity/wildbiodiversity_home.html |archivedate=6 February 2012  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.unsystem.org/SCN/archives/india/ch16.htm |title=United Nations, System of Organisations |publisher=Unsystem.org |year=2012 |accessdate=10 September 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|UN, system of organisations|2012}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502211218/http://www.unsystem.org/scn/archives/india/ch16.htm |archivedate=2 May 2012  }}\n* {{cite web |title=List of Municipalities in Tamil Nadu |url=http://www.tn.gov.in/cma/municipalities/municipalities_alphawise.html |publisher=Comm. of Municipal Admin., Govt. of Tamil Nadu |year=2011 |accessdate=7 September 2011 |ref={{sfnRef|List of municipalities in Tamil Nadu|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web |title=Elections to Local Bodies |url=http://tnsec.tn.nic.in/pdf/press_release_210911.pdf |publisher=Tamil State Election Commission |accessdate=28 October 2011 |year=2011 |ref={{sfnRef|Elections to local bodies|2011}} |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026221822/http://tnsec.tn.nic.in/pdf/press_release_210911.pdf |archivedate=26 October 2011  }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.tn.gov.in/district_statistics.html |accessdate=6 November 2011 |publisher=Government of Tamil Nadu |title=Districts of Tamil Nadu |year=2011 |ref={{sfnRef|Districts of Tamil Nadu|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.tnpolice.gov.in/ |title=Tamil Nadu Police |publisher=The Tamil Nadu Police |accessdate=4 July 2012 |ref={{sfnRef|Tamil Nadu Police|2011}} }}\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.tnpolice.gov.in/strength.html |title=Tamil Nadu Police |accessdate=4 July 2012 |publisher=The Tamil Nadu Police |ref={{sfnRef|TN Police strength|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web |title=Statistical Report of 2006 Tamil Nadu assembly results |publisher=Election Commission of India |url=http://eci.nic.in/eci_main/StatisticalReports/SE_2006/StatReport_TN_2006.pdf |year=2011 |ref={{sfnRef|Statistical Report of 2006 Tamil Nadu assembly results|2006}}}}\n* {{cite web |title=List of Successful candidates |publisher=Election Commission of India |url=http://eci.nic.in/eci_main/archiveofge2009/Stats/VOLI/11_ListOfSuccessfulCandidate.pdf |accessdate=4 July 2012 |year=2009 |ref={{sfnRef|List of Successful candidates|2009}}}}\n* {{cite web 